      • fNO_SPAWNING

        public static final CreateEntityFlags fNO_SPAWNING
        Do not spawn the created entity. This is intended to be used during activates, either from the DB or files, or when cloning OIs.

      • fIGNORE_MAX_CARDINALITY

        public static final CreateEntityFlags fIGNORE_MAX_CARDINALITY

      • fDONT_UPDATE_OI

        public static final CreateEntityFlags fDONT_UPDATE_OI
        Normally the create sets the Update flag for the OI. This flag prevents the Update flag from changing.

      • fIGNORE_PERMISSIONS

        public static final CreateEntityFlags fIGNORE_PERMISSIONS
        Ignore the CREATE flag permissions. Intended to be used by the DBHandler to create entities that are loaded from the DB.
